271
00:19:01,967 --> 00:19:06,000
I can't believe I'm coming back
<i> to this place again.</i>

272
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,500
<i> I have no choice.</i>

273
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:09,367
<i> We always have a choice.</i>

274
00:19:09,367 --> 00:19:13,800
<i>The right choice is to keep
what we did a secret</i>

275
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:15,633
<i>so there will still be
something left for Liam.</i>

276
00:19:15,633 --> 00:19:18,100
<i> Call Lieutenant Areza.</i>

277
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:19,933
<i> Turn me in to him.</i>

278
00:19:19,933 --> 00:19:21,600
[VAN DOOR SLIDES]

279
00:19:24,967 --> 00:19:25,967
<i> Emil.</i>

280
00:19:27,633 --> 00:19:28,767
<i> Man.</i>

281
00:19:29,967 --> 00:19:31,900
<i>I'm sorry for everything
that happened.</i>

282
00:19:34,067 --> 00:19:35,967
<i>We went through
a lot together, didn't we?</i>

283
00:19:36,933 --> 00:19:38,867
<i>Maybe we can still talk
this through?</i>

284
00:19:38,867 --> 00:19:40,567
<i> The police are on their way.</i>

285
00:19:40,567 --> 00:19:41,667
<i> You know, I thought</i>

286
00:19:41,667 --> 00:19:43,200
you wouldn't be able to turn in
<i> your own mother.</i>

287
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:46,433
<i>If you were in my position,
would you do the right thing?</i>

288
00:19:46,433 --> 00:19:47,833
<i> I didn't even get to know...</i>

289
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:51,000
my real father and now I'm going
<i> to lose my mother too?</i>

290
00:19:51,767 --> 00:19:54,000
That's why I can't turn her in.

291
00:19:54,833 --> 00:19:56,633
<i> I'll be separated from you...</i>

292
00:19:57,633 --> 00:19:58,900
<i> ...and your father.</i>

293
00:20:00,133 --> 00:20:02,733
<i> But I know you'll be okay.</i>

294
00:20:02,767 --> 00:20:04,800
<i> You'll be fine.</i>

295
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:07,133
<i> Is Homer my father?</i>

296
00:20:07,133 --> 00:20:10,667
<i>I didn't tell him that
I was pregnant with you.</i>

297
00:20:10,667 --> 00:20:13,767
<i>I saw how terrible
of a person he was.</i>

298
00:20:13,767 --> 00:20:17,533
<i>Pa, let's stop this before
we all end up destroyed.</i>

299
00:20:17,533 --> 00:20:18,767
<i> We're close, dear.</i>

300
00:20:19,933 --> 00:20:21,567
<i> One last mission.</i>

301
00:20:22,867 --> 00:20:25,200
<i>And that is to find
your sister Ayen.</i>

302
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:27,867
<i> Pa, seriously? Even now?</i>

303
00:20:27,867 --> 00:20:30,633
<i>Fine then, tell me where
we're supposed to find her.</i>

304
00:20:30,633 --> 00:20:32,533
<i> Magnus knows.</i>

305
00:20:32,533 --> 00:20:33,967
<i> I'll squeeze it out of him.</i>

306
00:20:33,967 --> 00:20:36,833
[SIREN WAILING]
